  "commit_message": "refactor(buildenv): reduce mutation ops from 2 nix builds to 1 (#4320)\n\n## Summary\n\n* Threads `out_link_prefix: Option<&Path>` through\n`transact_with_manifest` and `transact_with_lockfile_contents` so the\nsingle build inside each transaction creates activation symlinks\ndirectly via `nix build --out-link`.\n* Removes the separate outer `self.build(flox)?` call that previously\nran after every install/uninstall/edit/upgrade/include_upgrade in both\n`PathEnvironment` and `ManagedEnvironment`, replacin",
